00A0President-elect, he\u0027s definitely better than a Kerbal in office.\u00A0\u003Cimg alt=\u0022:cool:\u0022 data-emoticon=\u0022\u0022 src=\u0022//kerbal-forum-uploads.s3.us-west-2.amazonaws.com/emoticons/default_k_cool.gif\u0022 title=\u0022:cool:\u0022\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u003Cbr\u003E\u003Cimg alt=\u0022:D\u0022 data-emoticon=\u0022\u0022 src=\u0022//kerbal-forum-uploads.s3.us-west-2.amazonaws.com/emoticons/default_k_cheesy.gif\u0022 title=\u0022:D\u0022\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nAnd yeah, let\u0027s not get\u00A0into politics. Rules and everything.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Jeb!","CreatedById":159364,"CreatedDateTime":"2016-12-15T00:59:47Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00222888142\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022153533\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221481762989\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u0022142607\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022legoclone09\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\n53 minutes ago, legoclone09 said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u003Cbr\u003E\u003Cimg alt=\u0022:D\u0022 data-emoticon=\u0022\u0022 src=\u0022//kerbal-forum-uploads.s3.us-west-2.amazonaws.com/emoticons/default_k_cheesy.gif\u0022 title=\u0022:D\u0022\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nAnd yeah, let\u0027s not get\u00A0into politics. Rules and everything.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u003Cimg alt=\u0022:o\u0022 data-emoticon=\u0022\u0022 src=\u0022//kerbal-forum-uploads.s3.us-west-2.amazonaws.com/emoticons/ZNGIcon2.png\u0022 title=\u0022:o\u0022\u003E\u00A0Wait there\u0027s rules?\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nLol yes I know\u00A0\u003Cimg alt=\u0022:wink:\u0022 data-emoticon=\u0022\u0022 src=\u0022//kerbal-forum-uploads.s3.us-west-2.amazonaws.com/emoticons/default_k_wink.gif\u0022 title=\u0022;)\u0022\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cspan class=\u0022ipsType_reset ipsType_medium ipsType_light\u0022 data-excludequote=\u0022\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cstrong\u003EEdited \u003Ctime datetime=\u00222016-12-15T01:43:03Z\u0022 title=\u002212/15/2016 01:43  AM\u0022 data-short=\u00227 yr\u0022\u003EDecember 15, 2016\u003C/time\u003E by Jeb!\u003C/strong\u003E\n\u003C/span\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Tex_NL","CreatedById":58254,"CreatedDateTime":"2016-12-15T15:05:32Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nSeriously people? The guy asks about MechJeb and NOBODY even bothers to provide him with a link?\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Ciframe data-embedcontent=\u0022\u0022 frameborder=\u00220\u0022 src=\u0022https://forum.kerbalspaceprogram.com/index.php?/topic/111978-122-anatid-robotics-mumech-mechjeb-autopilot-260-12-dec-2016/\u0026amp;do=embed\u0022\u003E\u003C/iframe\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nDownload it, try it. And you\u0027ve got your answer.\u003Cbr\u003E\nIf you don\u0027t like it, uninstall it. Nothing gained, nothing lost.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Palaceviking","CreatedById":166883,"CreatedDateTime":"2016-12-15T15:30:34Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nIn short it hobbles your learning and the development of your piloting skill, \u00A0fun for a bit but I uninstalled it and went with engineer in the end.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"sarbian","CreatedById":57146,"CreatedDateTime":"2016-12-15T15:35:34Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nIts main feature is to create chaos on the forum by attracting people who will explain how you should play your solo game. And it also provides some useful in game feature like configurable displays, utilities and piloting assistant.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Avatarium","CreatedById":157403,"CreatedDateTime":"2016-12-15T23:12:55Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nQuick question(s): Is there a complete tutorial on youtub for Mechjeb? If so, I think it would help answer his question.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"genericeventhandler","CreatedById":149557,"CreatedDateTime":"2016-12-15T23:43:57Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nI always have it installed, but I use it less and less each time. The only thing that I use it for at the moment is delta v calcs and rendez-vous, because it\u0027s boring as hell to do.\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nThat said, I learnt most things from watching how mechjeb did it.\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Jeb!","CreatedById":159364,"CreatedDateTime":"2016-12-18T23:06:04Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00222888663\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022153533\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221481814332\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u002258254\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022Tex_NL\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\nOn 12/15/2016 at 10:05 AM, Tex_NL said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nSeriously people? The guy asks about MechJeb and NOBODY even bothers to provide him with a link?\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Ciframe data-embedcontent=\u0022\u0022 frameborder=\u00220\u0022 src=\u0022https://forum.kerbalspaceprogram.com/index.php?/topic/111978-122-anatid-robotics-mumech-mechjeb-autopilot-260-12-dec-2016/\u0026amp;do=embed\u0022\u003E\u003C/iframe\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nDownload it, try it. And you\u0027ve got your answer.\u003Cbr\u003E\nIf you don\u0027t like it, uninstall it. Nothing gained, nothing lost.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nThank you! Perfect timing, I\u0027m just now updating to 1.2.2.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00222888726\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022153533\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221481816134\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u002257146\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022sarbian\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\nOn 12/15/2016 at 10:35 AM, sarbian said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nIts main feature is to create chaos on the forum by attracting people who will explain how you should play your solo game. And it also provides some useful in game feature like configurable displays, utilities and piloting assistant.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nI\u0027ve played KSP enough now to understand fairly well how to pilot rockets\u00A0and aircraft. What I want now is to be able to take some of the difficulty and monotony away from escape and capturing burns. I spend way too much time fiddling with the orbit change thingy and it sucks up all my game time.\u00A0\u003Cimg alt=\u0022:P\u0022 data-emoticon=\u0022\u0022 src=\u0022//kerbal-forum-uploads.s3.us-west-2.amazonaws.com/emoticons/default_k_tongue.gif\u0022 title=\u0022:P\u0022\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\n"}]}